reviewText: Gave it to a friend for Christmas who was looking for Bruce Lee collection however it was out of stock everywhere. Luckily this seller shipped it fast too and it arrived right before the New Years. The DVD set came factory sealed like described and my buddy couldnt' get any happier.

bruce lee has always been my favorite action hero . thank you for this collection
great price for whole collection

Although the packaging shows Game of Death, the DVD itself is Game of Death II.  The set doesn't include the first one so if you over this set, be sure to verify you got what you ordered. Not impressed Amazon.

The only thing wrong with this collection was that I was expecting
"Game of Death" to include some of the lost footage of the Pagoda which it didn't and that is why i am giving this collection set a High 4 stars..

The rest of the movies were good.

What can you say about Bruce Lee's martial arts films that hasn't been said many times before?  They are still as good as they were when first released, even though movie making technology has advanced considerably since Lee's films were made.  A must have for all Bruce Lee fans and for martial arts enthusiasts in general.

Phil Humphries
Shodan, Laohu Kenpo
Fairfax, VA USA
